    <item>
      <title>加密货币繁荣之际，芝加哥期权交易所 (Cboe) 将推出以现金结算的比特币 ETF 期权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/cboe-to-launch-cash-settled-bitcoin-etf-options-as-crypto-booms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cboe Global Markets Inc. 表示，即将推出首个与比特币现货价格相关的现金结算指数期权，这是传统交易所新增加密货币相关证券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/cboe-to-launch-cash-settled-bitcoin-etf-options-as-crypto-booms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 16:32:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毕达哥拉斯加密基金回报率达 230%，超过比特币的涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/pythagoras-crypto-fund-returns-230-to-outpace-bitcoin-s-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[去年年底，Mitchell Dong 发现了一个机会：现货比特币 ETF 即将面向美国投资者推出，他希望自己的加密对冲基金能够提供表现更佳的竞争产品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/pythagoras-crypto-fund-returns-230-to-outpace-bitcoin-s-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 13:32:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gensler 退出计划导致美国证券交易委员会瞄准的加密代币数量激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/crypto-tokens-xrp-ada-sol-targeted-by-sec-jump-on-gensler-exit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国证券交易委员会主席、业界头号反对者加里·根斯勒 (Gary Gensler) 宣布计划辞职后，被美国证券交易委员会标记为未注册证券的数字资产正在上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/crypto-tokens-xrp-ada-sol-targeted-by-sec-jump-on-gensler-exit</guid>
